          "url": "https://daringfireball.net/2023/03/thorleifsson_musk_twitter",
          "title": "Phony Stark Picks on the Wrong Guy, Attempting (and of Course Botching) an HR Exit Interview Live on Twitter",
          "description": "Thorleifsson, to put it mildly, is a rather remarkable and inspiring person.",
          "author": null,
          "publisher": "Daring Fireball",
          "thumbnail": "https://daringfireball.net/graphics/df-square-1024.png",
          "icon": "https://daringfireball.net/graphics/apple-touch-icon.png"
        }
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "When celebrities get radicalised",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "koenig-heading",
        "tag": "h2",
        "version": 1,
        "renderVersion": "4.0"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The story of Russell Brand is a strange one. A decade or so he was a comedian and television presenter, who started getting plaudits for his forays into politics. And slowly, the presenting gigs and the movie appearances started to dry up (aside from voice acting, he didn't trouble the big screen much for half a decade, before he popped up again in Kenneth Branagh's ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Death on the Nile",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "). And, in the meantime, the politics became ever more extreme as his personal audience grow.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "He's beginning to look like another example of audience capture.  ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "bookmark",
        "url": "https://www.newstatesman.com/comment/2023/03/have-lost-russell-brand",
